                div
                    h2 Challenges and Reflection
                    p The four-week time constraint presented a challenge to our team. All of us had different schedules, took other classes, and some also had part-time work. We approached this by having clear role delegations, while still being flexible in assisting other team members when necessary. We adopted a more agile approach, simultaneously carrying out planning, design, and prototyping phases. This allowed us to complete the project in time.
                    p Through this project I familiarized myself with Figma, applied various design principles, and learned to improve my work through image treatment, font pairings, and layout design. It also taught me about design thinking methodologies and collaborating with a team in a short time. 


